The paper discusses a novel neural network paradigm for adversarial robustness, which falls under the broad category of deep learning. The paper specifically focuses on computer vision tasks, audio processing, and natural language processing, which are all subfields of computer science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
